<L>__{98. waist of the ship night}
<A>__{roaring flames, flying sparks, the clang of metal on metal. a forge has been set up. powder monkeys sweat on the bellows. the ship's blacksmith is churning out iron bolts, pintles and gudgeons, which are snatched away by nagel with tongs and thrown into a bucket of water to cool. a few yards away, wood chips fly from lamb's adze as the ship's massive new stern post takes shape. the new rudder is laid out flat, already cut to its final shape and being strengthened with great nails and iron bands which nehemiah slade and awkward davies are nailing into place. the hammering travels through the ship to...}
